WEBVTT

00:06.499 --> 00:07.840
(Respect copyright)

00:14.112 --> 00:20.704
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

00:24.288 --> 00:30.432
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

00:32.640 --> 00:35.872
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

00:36.096 --> 00:42.112
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

00:42.432 --> 00:45.856
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

00:45.920 --> 00:52.480
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

00:53.536 --> 00:57.472
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

00:57.472 --> 01:03.552
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

01:03.840 --> 01:07.712
ظآزPut every twist behind youظآز

01:07.712 --> 01:12.576
ظآزDrift leisurely through timeظآز

01:12.960 --> 01:15.680
ظآزMake headway against the windظآز

01:15.680 --> 01:18.667
ظآزLet mountains bow to your paceظآز

01:18.720 --> 01:24.128
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

01:24.640 --> 01:28.579
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

01:30.240 --> 01:34.490
=The First Jasmine=

01:35.344 --> 01:37.648
=Episode 30=

01:38.320 --> 01:41.960
Prince Ding, I wish
to make a deal with you.

01:44.281 --> 01:44.960
A deal?

01:45.800 --> 01:46.320
Yes.

01:51.320 --> 01:53.160
But I need you to swear an oath

01:54.401 --> 01:55.681
that as long as you live,

01:56.681 --> 01:59.041
you must ensure
my son Tianyang's safety.

02:00.600 --> 02:04.160
The Empress Dowager did not implicate
your family out of regard for old ties.

02:09.801 --> 02:11.081
I was in power for many years,

02:11.640 --> 02:13.640
and countless were defeated by me.

02:14.920 --> 02:16.480
Do you think my signed confession

02:17.281 --> 02:18.880
will settle this for good?

02:21.720 --> 02:22.416
No.

02:23.801 --> 02:27.480
The great calamity of my Zhou family
of Huaixi has just begun.

02:28.720 --> 02:31.720
So my son Tianyang cannot die.

02:35.320 --> 02:36.561
Why should I help you?

02:40.841 --> 02:43.121
Because I have a huge secret

02:44.241 --> 02:45.440
to tell you.

02:49.320 --> 02:52.320
Back then, your elder brother
and the Heiyun Cavalry were convicted

02:53.040 --> 02:55.521
of treason for entering
the capital without an edict.

02:56.320 --> 03:00.121
But it has been proven
that the edict did exist.

03:01.121 --> 03:04.200
And you indeed used
that edict to bring me down.

03:06.001 --> 03:07.401
Aren't you curious

03:09.401 --> 03:10.200
exactly who

03:11.200 --> 03:14.720
tricked the late emperor's edict
from your brother?

03:15.121 --> 03:18.241
Of course it was you
who instigated Dowager Consort Qin

03:18.920 --> 03:20.081
to trick away the edict.

03:20.081 --> 03:22.001
Your brother was no ordinary man.

03:22.801 --> 03:24.521
He knew it was his lifeline.

03:24.920 --> 03:26.920
Why would he just hand it
to me or Qin Zheng?

03:30.720 --> 03:33.880
Someone else tricked the edict from him.

03:34.600 --> 03:36.720
That person gained
your brother's complete trust.

03:37.040 --> 03:38.480
They took the edict

03:39.001 --> 03:40.600
and hid it immediately.

03:41.081 --> 03:43.200
Then they watched as your brother

03:43.200 --> 03:45.040
was framed and executed

03:45.640 --> 03:48.681
and as Heiyun Cavalry crumbled
and suffered heavy casualties.

03:50.561 --> 03:51.320
So?

03:52.241 --> 03:55.720
Don't you want to know
who that person was?

04:09.296 --> 04:12.944
(Vast as the Earth)

04:28.520 --> 04:31.561
Empress Dowager,
Zhou Jing has confessed.

04:35.681 --> 04:37.681
He met with Prince Ding today

04:37.760 --> 04:40.801
and then signed
and marked his confession.

04:43.520 --> 04:44.520
What did he say?

04:46.241 --> 04:47.921
He asked to clear the room.

04:48.280 --> 04:51.121
No one else was present
but a confidant of Prince Ding.

04:59.681 --> 05:00.681
There is one more thing.

05:02.520 --> 05:05.481
Zhou Tianyang is still kneeling
outside the palace.

05:05.921 --> 05:07.080
It has been two days already.

06:04.520 --> 06:05.320
Father.

06:07.840 --> 06:08.361
Father.

06:10.361 --> 06:10.960
Tianyang,

06:12.681 --> 06:13.681
why are you here?

06:14.640 --> 06:16.640
I... I came to see you, Father.

06:17.440 --> 06:18.400
How are you?

06:19.001 --> 06:21.320
Have they treated you badly? Have you...

06:21.320 --> 06:23.041
Didn't I tell you to go back to Lingnan?

06:23.200 --> 06:24.721
Why are you still in the capital?

06:26.121 --> 06:29.721
You're in danger. How can I just leave?

06:30.801 --> 06:32.840
Staying here won't help.

06:33.080 --> 06:34.921
Who says? Look.

06:35.880 --> 06:37.840
I knelt outside the palace for two days,

06:37.880 --> 06:39.481
begging for the Empress Dowager's mercy.

06:39.880 --> 06:41.880
Today, Eunuch Shunxi
personally gave me this.

06:41.880 --> 06:44.400
I've checked. Inside are fine wine
and delicious food.

06:44.400 --> 06:47.080
Father, the Empress Dowager
still cares about you deep down.

06:48.320 --> 06:49.880
At the next interrogation,

06:50.080 --> 06:53.001
be sure to be honest
and confess voluntarily.

06:53.041 --> 06:54.080
Don't resist.

06:54.801 --> 06:58.041
Perhaps out of old sentiment
and your merits, the Empress Dowager

06:58.200 --> 07:00.121
will be pleased and pardon you.

07:07.640 --> 07:10.921
Father, what's wrong?

07:11.921 --> 07:13.080
Are you feeling unwell?

07:21.200 --> 07:21.721
No.

07:24.400 --> 07:25.041
That's good.

07:32.440 --> 07:35.200
Tianyang, listen to me.

07:37.400 --> 07:40.200
My affairs involve many people.

07:41.200 --> 07:43.080
There won't be a quick resolution.

07:44.041 --> 07:46.320
Your mom is in poor health.

07:47.561 --> 07:50.440
If she knows this,
she might not survive it.

07:51.400 --> 07:54.280
Hurry back to Lingnan
and take good care of her.

07:55.080 --> 07:57.601
It's more useful than staying
in the capital, understand?

07:59.001 --> 08:02.601
Father, what about you then?

08:03.280 --> 08:04.041
Tianyang,

08:07.320 --> 08:11.080
you've been spoiled by your mom
since childhood.

08:12.001 --> 08:13.041
Your nature is simple.

08:15.361 --> 08:17.121
It's my fault for not teaching you well.

08:20.760 --> 08:21.440
That's not true.

08:24.041 --> 08:27.320
In the past, I always thought

08:28.320 --> 08:29.520
that with me protecting you,

08:30.880 --> 08:33.241
it wouldn't matter
even if you were unruly all your life.

08:35.081 --> 08:36.040
But from now on...

08:37.640 --> 08:39.880
Let's not talk about this, Father.

08:40.241 --> 08:42.601
We haven't reached
the end of our rope yet.

08:42.961 --> 08:45.481
I... I wrote to Qin Zheng.

08:46.481 --> 08:48.001
The Empress Dowager trusts her most.

08:48.920 --> 08:50.880
She can surely save you once she's back.

08:50.880 --> 08:51.601
Enough.

08:53.601 --> 08:55.520
Time's up. You should leave.

08:55.880 --> 08:56.721
Listen to me.

08:57.520 --> 08:59.321
I will definitely get you out of here.

09:00.321 --> 09:01.721
When you get out,

09:02.001 --> 09:04.081
let's go back to Lingnan
and live together, alright?

09:05.040 --> 09:06.280
I've grown up.

09:06.640 --> 09:08.721
I can take good care of you and Mom.

09:09.481 --> 09:11.961
Then our family of three
will be happy together, alright?

09:11.961 --> 09:13.040
- Go!
- Alright.

09:13.241 --> 09:14.201
- Father.
- Hurry!

09:16.280 --> 09:18.520
Father! Father!

09:18.920 --> 09:21.160
Father! Father!

09:22.880 --> 09:24.961
Wait for me. Just wait!

09:25.584 --> 09:26.096
Let's go.

09:26.096 --> 09:27.001
- I will.
- Wait for me!

11:10.640 --> 11:14.081
Your Majesty, Marquis Muyang has died.

11:29.081 --> 11:32.241
Your Highness, did you make
this straw doll?

11:37.241 --> 11:39.040
It's getting late.

11:39.241 --> 11:41.441
Why not rest early?
Don't wait any longer.

11:42.321 --> 11:43.601
What time is it now?

11:44.441 --> 11:45.648
A quarter past the Zi hour.

11:57.001 --> 11:58.081
- Li!
- Ms. Wen.

11:58.081 --> 11:58.841
Li!

11:59.441 --> 12:00.841
What's the rush? What happened?

12:01.321 --> 12:04.400
Yao... Yao sent word that...

12:04.841 --> 12:07.081
He said... He said...

12:07.321 --> 12:08.560
Zhou Jing is dead!

12:09.880 --> 12:11.001
He's dead.

12:12.241 --> 12:16.400
Li, our revenge is fulfilled.

12:16.841 --> 12:17.880
He's dead.

12:18.241 --> 12:21.800
Li, he's dead. He's dead.

12:23.400 --> 12:24.848
It's over!

12:30.920 --> 12:32.272
It's over!

12:35.800 --> 12:39.441
Yes, it's over.

12:42.721 --> 12:43.640
It's over.

13:05.640 --> 13:07.721
Your Highness hasn't returned yet?

13:09.721 --> 13:10.520
Your Highness,

13:12.400 --> 13:14.481
now that Marquis Muyang is dead,

13:14.560 --> 13:16.368
your household, the Heiyun Cavalry,

13:16.464 --> 13:19.800
and the late Prince Ding's injustice
will soon be revealed to the world.

13:20.241 --> 13:22.560
The wrongs will be righted,
and evil will be purged.

13:22.560 --> 13:25.721
Congratulations, Your Highness.

13:32.400 --> 13:33.920
Your Highness bore it for eight years.

13:34.121 --> 13:37.241
I know best the bitterness of it all.

13:38.081 --> 13:41.321
From now on, you and we can all

13:41.400 --> 13:44.400
truly live for ourselves.

13:44.601 --> 13:46.121
On this joyous day,

13:46.321 --> 13:50.241
I originally wished
to have a good drink with you.

13:50.680 --> 13:53.081
But it's getting late.

13:53.321 --> 13:55.680
Your Highness should go home now.

13:55.680 --> 13:58.121
After all, Her Highness
has suffered a lot this time,

13:58.121 --> 14:00.441
enduring so much fear and worry.
It hasn't been easy.

14:00.441 --> 14:02.121
Now that the matter has settled...

14:02.121 --> 14:02.920
Revenue Clerk Gu.

14:04.321 --> 14:07.920
You and Her Highness will surely
live in harmony from now on

14:07.920 --> 14:09.560
and enjoy a peaceful and stable life.

14:09.560 --> 14:10.321
Revenue Clerk Gu!

14:13.040 --> 14:13.841
Revenue Clerk Gu,

14:14.880 --> 14:17.201
it's getting late.
Why don't you go back first?

14:23.520 --> 14:25.081
Although Marquis Muyang has fallen,

14:25.168 --> 14:27.184
Imperial Court of Judicial Review
isn't clean yet.

14:27.520 --> 14:28.721
Tomorrow will be a busy day.

14:30.201 --> 14:32.081
You have a fair point.

14:32.640 --> 14:33.520
Then, Your Highness,

14:33.640 --> 14:36.520
I must have a good drink with you
some other day.

14:36.520 --> 14:38.680
You mustn't refuse me then.

14:40.321 --> 14:41.520
I take my leave.

14:53.321 --> 14:54.121
Your Highness,

14:56.880 --> 14:57.800
shall we return?

15:04.601 --> 15:05.640
I'll go get the carriage.

15:57.880 --> 16:00.040
Your Highness, the carriage is ready.

16:02.321 --> 16:03.121
Your Highness?

16:06.201 --> 16:07.001
Your Highness!

16:16.961 --> 16:18.800
Physician, how is he?

16:19.841 --> 16:20.800
Let's talk outside.

16:35.201 --> 16:36.321
(If it weren't for her,)

16:37.040 --> 16:39.824
your brother could have stalled
until Duke Hua's return.

16:41.560 --> 16:42.280
Who?

16:43.520 --> 16:46.560
Xu Wanzhou of Lishan Academy.

16:47.201 --> 16:48.241
Say that again.

16:50.081 --> 16:53.280
The one who tricked the edict
from your brother Mo Xiuwen,

16:53.280 --> 16:54.560
causing his tragic death

16:55.800 --> 16:58.920
and bringing unjust blame upon
the Heiyun Cavalry and your household,

16:58.920 --> 17:00.721
was none other than your wife's mother,

17:02.001 --> 17:03.040
Xu Wanzhou.

17:06.280 --> 17:08.481
Just ramblings of a dying man.

17:09.560 --> 17:11.560
You know well whether
it's ramblings or not.

17:12.921 --> 17:14.961
In such a critical situation back then,

17:15.161 --> 17:16.656
aside from a Lishan Academy member,

17:17.280 --> 17:20.760
who else could have made him willingly

17:20.881 --> 17:22.881
hand over that life-saving edict?

17:26.480 --> 17:27.312
Your brother

17:28.080 --> 17:30.760
probably even regarded her
as a great savior.

17:32.120 --> 17:33.401
But that's understandable.

17:33.881 --> 17:36.641
After all, Lishan Academy
is a top institution of letters

17:37.201 --> 17:39.360
and has always stayed
out of factional strife.

17:39.721 --> 17:40.881
Its status is transcendent.

17:41.401 --> 17:42.401
If it'd been me,

17:43.681 --> 17:45.760
I would've probably
been fooled by her as well.

17:50.080 --> 17:50.921
What?

17:51.881 --> 17:52.721
Has your wife

17:53.641 --> 17:56.280
never told you
a single one of these things?

18:00.721 --> 18:04.208
I originally thought
you were magnanimous.

18:05.681 --> 18:07.481
It turns out you had no idea at all.

18:09.560 --> 18:12.961
Ever since your wife married
into your household,

18:14.201 --> 18:15.961
you must have been
living quite comfortably.

18:17.232 --> 18:20.001
Newly wed and deeply in love.

18:20.760 --> 18:23.312
Even your crippled legs
of many years were healed.

18:25.120 --> 18:26.560
Have you never thought?

18:27.600 --> 18:29.104
Did she truly want to marry you?

18:33.201 --> 18:36.520
Or was it out of guilt,
wanting to compensate you?

18:44.120 --> 18:47.320
Prince Ding, you are so astute.

18:47.800 --> 18:50.921
Have you never taken a good look
at your other half?

18:51.120 --> 18:54.921
Is the look in her eyes
genuine love or guilt?

18:55.401 --> 18:56.201
Shut up!

18:56.961 --> 18:59.760
After all, her mother
owes your family a life.

18:59.760 --> 19:01.232
- Shut up!
- And 30,000 lives of Heiyun Cavalry!

19:12.001 --> 19:13.481
Just wait for your doom.

19:33.481 --> 19:36.401
(Yao, have I ever told you?)

19:37.681 --> 19:38.921
This time down the mountain,

19:40.401 --> 19:42.280
I have so many things to do.

19:43.881 --> 19:45.241
What things?

19:49.881 --> 19:51.840
I want to eat lots of good food.

19:53.360 --> 19:56.241
I want to take back my mom's shop.

19:58.080 --> 19:59.641
I also want to find my seniors.

20:01.721 --> 20:02.520
And...

20:03.921 --> 20:05.584
And help that senior chop down the tree.

20:09.520 --> 20:10.704
Already done.

20:13.560 --> 20:14.704
And help you stand up

20:16.760 --> 20:18.032
and make you live happily.

20:24.144 --> 20:26.288
ظآزWhy do you panicظآز

20:27.152 --> 20:30.224
ظآزFor no reason,
you pushed me away and left meظآز

20:30.864 --> 20:33.680
ظآزAfraid we might start againظآز

20:33.872 --> 20:37.712
ظآزChanging many things, right or wrongظآز

20:38.352 --> 20:41.168
ظآزFate is blurred and bewilderingظآز

20:41.560 --> 20:44.961
They stole a very important item
from my mom.

20:46.120 --> 20:47.481
Have you found the item now?

20:48.881 --> 20:50.080
I have some leads.

20:52.752 --> 20:55.632
ظآزAmidst life's ups and downs,
turns and twistsظآز

20:55.632 --> 20:59.760
ظآزLove has never strayed awayظآز

21:00.528 --> 21:02.320
ظآزThroughout this lifetimeظآز

21:02.320 --> 21:06.768
ظآزIn the end, we're together againظآز

21:07.280 --> 21:10.448
ظآزCountless trials and pleadings,
right or wrongظآز

21:10.448 --> 21:15.056
ظآزTry to make this love quietظآز

21:15.600 --> 21:17.296
ظآزBut we fight backظآز

21:20.040 --> 21:23.441
Your Highness,
you haven't slept all night?

21:25.280 --> 21:26.560
His Highness hasn't returned?

21:27.721 --> 21:28.600
Not yet.

21:28.921 --> 21:31.520
Didn't they say Marquis Muyang
committed suicide in prison?

21:31.520 --> 21:34.080
With such a big event,
he must have been busy.

21:35.961 --> 21:37.401
Even when he was busy before,

21:38.120 --> 21:39.921
he would send someone to inform me.

21:39.961 --> 21:42.520
Well, maybe he was just too busy

21:42.520 --> 21:43.481
and never got to it.

21:45.721 --> 21:46.520
Is that so?

21:48.241 --> 21:49.040
It must be.

21:50.921 --> 21:51.760
That makes sense.

21:54.681 --> 21:56.641
Jin, you're back.

21:58.352 --> 22:00.944
ظآزThe eyes are still clearظآز

22:03.344 --> 22:05.328
ظآزNone better than you,
and none better than meظآز

22:08.080 --> 22:09.360
His Highness hasn't come back?

22:10.760 --> 22:13.201
No, His Highness
has official business to attend to.

22:13.360 --> 22:14.641
He sent me back for some things.

22:15.441 --> 22:17.441
Why do you smell
so strongly of medicine?

22:19.320 --> 22:21.441
Do I? I don't smell it.

22:21.881 --> 22:23.800
Did His Highness say
when he would return?

22:26.881 --> 22:27.472
No.

22:27.600 --> 22:28.641
Then I'll go find him.

22:28.721 --> 22:29.320
Your Highness,

22:31.241 --> 22:32.800
you'd better wait in the mansion.

22:33.641 --> 22:35.201
When His Highness is due back,

22:36.441 --> 22:37.681
he will come back.

22:39.600 --> 22:40.208
You...

22:42.520 --> 22:45.441
(If you are around, I can be braver.)

22:47.201 --> 22:48.161
Then I'll accompany you.

22:49.441 --> 22:50.481
It's a deal then.

22:50.881 --> 22:53.120
No matter what path you take,

22:53.921 --> 22:56.641
smooth or thorny,

22:57.641 --> 22:58.681
(I'll be with you.)

22:59.241 --> 23:00.816
(You won't be alone anymore.)

23:02.320 --> 23:03.360
(I'll always be with you.)

23:04.272 --> 23:07.568
ظآزAmidst life's ups and downs,
turns and twistsظآز

23:07.568 --> 23:12.176
ظآزLove has never strayed awayظآز

23:12.176 --> 23:13.936
ظآزThroughout this lifetimeظآز

23:13.936 --> 23:18.128
ظآزIn the end, we're together againظآز

23:19.024 --> 23:22.096
ظآزCountless trials and pleadings,
right or wrongظآز

23:22.096 --> 23:26.704
ظآزTry to make this love quietظآز

23:27.216 --> 23:28.880
ظآزBut we fight backظآز

23:31.120 --> 23:32.721
(But Qingshuang
has always been with me.)

23:34.481 --> 23:37.600
I will always be with you, alright?

23:39.001 --> 23:39.800
Alright.

23:40.336 --> 23:44.048
ظآزSilently, we turn pain into joyظآز

23:44.048 --> 23:45.456
ظآزYou reach out and pull meظآز

23:45.456 --> 23:47.632
ظآزAnd I gently touchظآز

23:47.632 --> 23:49.200
ظآزSmooth out the creasesظآز

23:49.200 --> 23:52.944
ظآزSo we can tightly fit togetherظآز

23:52.944 --> 23:55.920
ظآزWithout you, there's no meظآز

23:56.048 --> 23:58.672
ظآزPassing by the worldظآز

23:58.672 --> 24:00.208
ظآزPart of my broken selfظآز

24:00.208 --> 24:02.384
ظآزFinds our places in an embraceظآز

24:02.384 --> 24:03.952
ظآزFulfilling our wishesظآز

24:04.208 --> 24:08.752
ظآزLovers remain calm and composedظآز

24:09.584 --> 24:11.600
ظآزNone better than you,
and none better than meظآز

24:11.760 --> 24:19.536
ظآزLove blooms at every spring and sunsetظآز

24:35.408 --> 24:37.641
(To the Chancellery:
By Heaven's Mandate for the sovereign.)

24:37.641 --> 24:40.320
(Marquis Muyang Zhou Jing
formed cliques for personal gain,)

24:40.320 --> 24:43.161
(stole military weapons,
colluded with Cangbei,)

24:43.161 --> 24:44.760
(betrayed the country,)

24:45.360 --> 24:47.280
(and even concealed
the late emperor's edict,)

24:47.721 --> 24:50.520
(causing loyalists to be wronged
and the nation to be in turmoil.)

24:50.520 --> 24:53.560
(His crimes are heinous
and too numerous to record.)

24:54.401 --> 24:57.600
(He committed suicide out of fear,
bringing his own ruin.)

24:57.600 --> 25:00.241
(Considering that he had
some minor merits carried on,)

25:00.280 --> 25:03.600
(all those who were unaware,
not involved, and not accomplices)

25:03.600 --> 25:05.320
(are exempt from collective punishment.)

25:05.320 --> 25:07.360
Their estates shall be seized,

25:07.600 --> 25:09.681
(Changxing Gate)
titles revoked, and stripped of rank.

25:09.961 --> 25:12.800
They shall be reduced to commoners,
forever disgraced

25:12.881 --> 25:14.288
and barred from office.

25:15.360 --> 25:17.520
(The Heiyun Cavalry served
with loyalty and valor,)

25:17.641 --> 25:19.040
(earning great battle honors.)

25:19.080 --> 25:21.721
(They're now fully restored
in reputation.)

25:22.161 --> 25:24.161
The late Prince Ding, Mo Xiuwen,

25:24.360 --> 25:27.161
diligently performed
his duties with utmost loyalty.

25:27.481 --> 25:31.441
(Jingzhao Prefecture)
His title's restored to honor his valor.

25:37.360 --> 25:38.161
Your Highness.

25:55.520 --> 25:56.080
Your Highness.

25:56.840 --> 25:57.520
What is it?

25:59.441 --> 26:00.360
Ms. Wen says

26:00.360 --> 26:03.961
it will be the death anniversary
of Master Xiuwen in two days.

26:03.961 --> 26:07.040
She wants to visit the grave
and asks if you'd like to go too.

26:08.336 --> 26:09.280
The day after tomorrow?

26:09.280 --> 26:10.080
Yes.

26:13.320 --> 26:15.560
Tell her that I will go.

26:16.641 --> 26:17.520
Yes.

26:18.760 --> 26:20.721
Also, Ms. Wen asks

26:21.161 --> 26:22.760
when Your Highness will return home.

26:23.840 --> 26:26.161
No matter how busy
the official duties are,

26:26.241 --> 26:27.560
you can't just not come home.

26:27.881 --> 26:29.881
Her Highness has been waiting
for you for days

26:29.881 --> 26:31.120
and has lost her appetite.

26:31.360 --> 26:33.241
She has lost much weight.

26:39.961 --> 26:42.600
Tell Ms. Wen not to worry.

26:43.441 --> 26:44.760
I'll come back once I'm done.

26:45.961 --> 26:46.760
Yes.

27:10.224 --> 27:17.104
(Tomb of Lord Mo Xiuwen)

27:38.360 --> 27:39.161
Xiuwen,

27:41.280 --> 27:42.641
we've come to see you.

27:43.840 --> 27:46.080
And we've brought you good news.

27:48.600 --> 27:52.201
That edict has been found.

27:54.120 --> 27:57.401
Our household and the Heiyun Cavalry
have been cleared in reputation.

27:59.080 --> 28:00.241
And Zhou Jing is dead.

28:01.080 --> 28:03.280
Good and evil always meet their due.

28:03.961 --> 28:07.280
But it took too long for that to happen.

28:07.881 --> 28:09.760
You've been down there
for so many years.

28:11.080 --> 28:12.840
You must have been waiting anxiously.

28:19.840 --> 28:21.520
The soldiers of the Heiyun Cavalry

28:22.520 --> 28:24.161
have also been cleared of their charges.

28:25.600 --> 28:28.481
Those still in the army
have been restored to their posts.

28:29.840 --> 28:33.520
Those who lost their positions
have received silver as compensation.

28:34.441 --> 28:37.641
For the deceased, their families
can report to the authorities.

28:38.120 --> 28:41.161
The court will distribute compensation
to their parents, wives, and children.

28:42.096 --> 28:43.120
Mom,

28:44.432 --> 28:46.241
Father has been exonerated.

28:46.921 --> 28:48.881
Why are you still unhappy?

28:49.360 --> 28:50.921
I'm not unhappy.

28:52.360 --> 28:54.800
But you keep shedding tears.

28:56.921 --> 29:00.800
One can cry even when they're happy.

29:03.001 --> 29:04.641
I just feel that

29:06.040 --> 29:09.921
eight years is too long,
and things have changed so much.

29:11.760 --> 29:13.201
Some people can wait and see it.

29:14.921 --> 29:15.600
And some

29:17.800 --> 29:19.201
will never be able to see it.

29:28.681 --> 29:30.881
Wuyou, go with Jin and Steward Cui

29:30.881 --> 29:32.800
to fetch some water
from the nearby stream.

29:33.616 --> 29:34.384
- Yes.
- Yes.

29:37.840 --> 29:38.641
Let's go.

29:42.721 --> 29:46.080
This matter can be
considered settled, right?

29:50.921 --> 29:51.721
Yao?

29:53.401 --> 29:56.641
Did you have a fight with Li?

30:01.760 --> 30:04.600
She has been looking
very unwell these past few days.

30:05.360 --> 30:08.760
She eats very little
and has lost a lot of weight.

30:10.560 --> 30:12.961
She has no close family
of her own by her side.

30:13.560 --> 30:16.520
She's been through so much pain

30:16.721 --> 30:18.080
and suffering lately.

30:20.241 --> 30:22.120
Please don't mistreat her.

30:25.441 --> 30:26.080
I understand.

30:31.120 --> 30:33.241
When I first married your brother,

30:33.641 --> 30:34.921
I was still young.

30:35.080 --> 30:36.760
He was always away with the army.

30:37.401 --> 30:39.921
We hardly saw each other
a few times a year.

30:41.840 --> 30:45.001
He was dull and didn't like to talk.

30:46.241 --> 30:49.560
At that time, I really didn't like him.

30:50.600 --> 30:53.120
And I was certain
he didn't care about me either.

30:54.641 --> 30:57.080
Several times I went home
and cried to my mother,

30:58.681 --> 30:59.961
wanting to divorce.

31:02.681 --> 31:05.800
Then later, he got into trouble.

31:07.001 --> 31:09.080
From imprisonment to execution,

31:10.120 --> 31:12.001
it was only a short two months.

31:12.241 --> 31:13.800
It felt like a dream.

31:15.840 --> 31:19.401
Before I could realize, he was gone.

31:22.320 --> 31:25.800
After he died,
I received a letter from him.

31:26.161 --> 31:27.401
When I opened it,

31:29.401 --> 31:31.080
I found a letter of divorce.

31:32.800 --> 31:34.961
The last thing that clumsy-tongued man

31:35.161 --> 31:37.040
wanted to say to me

31:38.992 --> 31:40.800
was to divorce me.

31:42.120 --> 31:43.800
Xiuwen didn't want to implicate you.

31:44.320 --> 31:48.040
Yes, and that's when I realized

31:48.760 --> 31:51.840
that he truly cared for me.

31:54.201 --> 31:55.001
Unfortunately,

31:57.552 --> 31:58.681
it was too late.

32:00.360 --> 32:01.161
Yao,

32:02.641 --> 32:05.481
this is all there is
for your brother and me.

32:06.120 --> 32:09.001
But you and Li are still young.
Don't be like us.

32:10.560 --> 32:13.320
Whatever you have to say, say it.

32:14.241 --> 32:18.001
Don't wait until she is gone
to cherish her.

32:30.481 --> 32:31.721
(Fine Wine)
My lady, you're here.

32:31.721 --> 32:32.241
Yes.

32:32.721 --> 32:34.840
Your requested seat
from last time is ready for you.

32:35.840 --> 32:37.201
You're here for the story too?

32:37.201 --> 32:38.001
Yes.

32:38.241 --> 32:39.481
You're here. Hurry.

32:39.481 --> 32:40.681
My lady, your food.

32:40.681 --> 32:41.201
Just in time.

32:41.201 --> 32:42.064
Feel free to call me.

32:43.320 --> 32:45.881
Your Highness, please eat something.

32:45.881 --> 32:48.040
You haven't been
eating properly these days.

32:53.320 --> 32:57.040
Your Highness, why exactly
did we come here today?

32:59.201 --> 33:00.144
To listen to a story.

33:03.840 --> 33:04.681
Coming!

33:05.241 --> 33:06.641
You are seriously carefree.

33:07.001 --> 33:09.040
His Highness hasn't returned
for several days.

33:09.040 --> 33:10.681
You're still in the mood for a story?

33:14.120 --> 33:16.201
Last time we left off,

33:16.760 --> 33:21.961
Madam Liu forced Liu Sanlang
to divorce Lady Meng.

33:23.241 --> 33:27.641
A loving young couple
was forced to part.

33:28.080 --> 33:30.001
It was heart-wrenching.

33:30.840 --> 33:33.241
Lady Meng returned to her maiden home.

33:33.560 --> 33:35.280
But her snobbish elder brother

33:35.441 --> 33:40.481
forced her to remarry a wealthy man
from the neighboring village.

33:40.881 --> 33:43.320
With no way out, Lady Meng

33:43.320 --> 33:46.600
asked a neighbor
to send a letter to Liu Sanlang.

33:47.641 --> 33:48.520
Hearing the news,

33:48.520 --> 33:51.481
Liu Sanlang couldn't stand it
and went to rescue her at once.

33:51.760 --> 33:53.401
Just then,

33:54.320 --> 33:56.201
Madam Liu stopped him

33:56.201 --> 33:59.840
and told him
the cause of his father's death.

34:00.560 --> 34:02.320
Only then did Liu Sanlang learn

34:02.520 --> 34:03.481
that his beloved wife,

34:03.520 --> 34:07.241
whom he cherished like a treasure,

34:07.360 --> 34:11.401
was actually the younger sister
of his father's murderer.

34:11.961 --> 34:14.361
He stood frozen on the spot,

34:14.640 --> 34:19.080
and his feet could no longer
step out of the gate.

34:19.481 --> 34:21.361
(Liu Sanlang's father died
in corv├رe labor,)

34:21.600 --> 34:24.240
and Lady Meng's brother
was the overseer at that time.

34:24.841 --> 34:26.080
That was the root of it.

34:26.881 --> 34:29.040
And Liu Sanlang is a filial son,

34:29.321 --> 34:31.481
unable to defy his mother.

34:32.120 --> 34:33.200
There was no chance.

34:35.240 --> 34:37.001
On the day of the wedding,

34:38.040 --> 34:41.120
Lady Meng waited in vain
for Liu Sanlang.

34:41.281 --> 34:43.680
She only saw the golden carriage
and jade wheels,

34:43.881 --> 34:46.801
a bridal procession
with red silk and brocade,

34:46.801 --> 34:48.881
coming in a grand display.

34:49.441 --> 34:52.281
Lady Meng's heart was broken.

34:52.481 --> 34:54.560
She knew their vows had come to nothing.

34:54.841 --> 34:57.801
So she removed her hairpin,
gathered her skirt,

34:57.881 --> 34:59.600
and jumped into the river.

35:00.600 --> 35:03.281
Alas, what a tragedy.

35:05.240 --> 35:06.040
She died?

35:07.001 --> 35:10.080
When the news of Lady Meng's death came,

35:10.240 --> 35:12.881
Liu Sanlang felt
as if struck by lightning

35:12.881 --> 35:14.001
and vomited blood.

35:14.281 --> 35:18.961
He stumbled to the pavilion
where they had parted

35:19.560 --> 35:21.560
and shouted at the sky.

35:23.401 --> 35:25.680
He cursed fate for toying with them,

35:25.801 --> 35:28.680
preventing lovers from staying together,

35:29.040 --> 35:31.961
and hated himself
for breaking their vows,

35:32.001 --> 35:33.761
causing his wife's death.

35:34.401 --> 35:37.600
So he hung a white silk cloth
from the pavilion

35:37.801 --> 35:41.520
and ended his life.

35:43.441 --> 35:45.441
Truly a pair of ill-fated lovers.

35:47.481 --> 35:48.680
As the saying goes,

35:49.321 --> 35:52.761
the underworld forbids
branches to entwine;

35:53.520 --> 35:56.961
the heavens find no trace
of paired wings' sound.

35:57.160 --> 35:59.560
The cruelest is the heartless sky,

36:00.361 --> 36:06.481
as two lonely graves
share the same moonlight.

36:41.168 --> 36:46.288
(Prince Ding's Mansion)

36:53.481 --> 36:55.120
Your Highness, you're back.

36:56.881 --> 36:58.720
His Highness is back. He's in your room.

37:01.801 --> 37:02.961
You all go ahead.

37:03.680 --> 37:04.481
Yes.

37:46.361 --> 37:47.841
Haven't you been sleeping well?

37:48.921 --> 37:50.321
You've got dark circles.

37:52.001 --> 37:54.120
Busy with official duties,
but it's fine.

37:58.481 --> 37:59.520
Marquis Muyang is dead.

38:02.361 --> 38:03.281
I know.

38:05.841 --> 38:06.961
Before he died,

38:07.801 --> 38:10.160
he told me some things about your mom.

38:12.640 --> 38:14.281
I want to know if they're true.

38:16.881 --> 38:17.841
What things?

38:22.200 --> 38:23.120
If I ask you,

38:24.441 --> 38:26.281
will you tell me the truth?

38:28.680 --> 38:29.600
I will.

38:30.600 --> 38:31.401
Back then,

38:33.401 --> 38:35.481
was it your mom who tricked the edict

38:36.520 --> 38:38.160
from my brother?

38:47.720 --> 38:48.281
Yes.

38:52.040 --> 38:53.801
But she didn't do it intentionally.

38:55.240 --> 38:57.801
Back then, the late emperor passed away.

38:58.281 --> 38:59.801
The Eastern Palace was burned down.

39:00.841 --> 39:02.441
And your brother was in prison.

39:03.200 --> 39:05.961
The one presiding over his case
was Marquis Muyang.

39:08.441 --> 39:11.321
Your brother claimed he entered
the capital by an edict,

39:12.001 --> 39:13.881
but he refused to produce the edict.

39:14.961 --> 39:16.801
He was determined to wait for Duke Hua.

39:19.841 --> 39:21.560
My mom was deceived.

39:22.361 --> 39:25.841
She got the location
of the edict from your brother.

39:30.040 --> 39:31.160
She wanted to save him

39:33.080 --> 39:34.441
but ended up causing his death.

39:35.560 --> 39:37.281
So regarding this matter,

39:39.441 --> 39:41.240
your mom never hid it from you?

39:43.361 --> 39:45.600
You've known all along, haven't you?

39:49.720 --> 39:50.520
Haven't you?

39:56.281 --> 39:59.040
Yes, I have.

40:02.120 --> 40:03.600
Then why didn't you tell me earlier?

40:05.160 --> 40:07.361
I was afraid you would
drive me away if I told you.

40:09.520 --> 40:11.240
Before your brother was executed,

40:12.001 --> 40:13.680
I went to see him on behalf of my mom.

40:14.160 --> 40:15.281
I promised him

40:16.281 --> 40:17.761
that Lishan Academy would clear

40:17.761 --> 40:20.200
his, his family's,
and Heiyun Cavalry's names

40:20.881 --> 40:22.441
and that I would heal your legs

40:23.361 --> 40:26.240
to repay my mom's debt
and compensate you.

40:26.720 --> 40:27.520
Repay a debt?

40:33.200 --> 40:34.001
Compensate?

40:47.961 --> 40:49.520
My brother was wronged for eight years.

40:51.441 --> 40:53.600
My sister-in-law
became a widow overnight.

40:55.761 --> 40:57.801
Wuyou lost his father at a young age.

40:58.801 --> 41:00.520
Thirty thousand Heiyun Cavalry soldiers

41:01.560 --> 41:04.881
followed my brother to death.

41:05.600 --> 41:07.160
Tens of thousands of soldiers

41:09.441 --> 41:11.080
suffered unjust accusations.

41:14.040 --> 41:16.401
How many families were torn apart?

41:17.680 --> 41:19.200
And how many parents

41:19.921 --> 41:21.881
had to bury their own children?

41:23.040 --> 41:24.761
I can't appreciate
your mother's struggles

41:25.720 --> 41:27.520
on behalf of those people.

41:42.200 --> 41:43.520
As for myself,

41:46.560 --> 41:47.881
I am very grateful to you.

41:49.520 --> 41:51.520
I thank you for healing my legs

41:53.200 --> 41:56.160
and for giving a cripple
like me a chance to live.

42:00.040 --> 42:01.441
You came to my side

42:03.240 --> 42:06.680
to compensate and pay a debt.

42:10.441 --> 42:11.841
I should be grateful to you.

42:12.600 --> 42:13.441
That's not true.

42:32.144 --> 42:34.992
(Preview)

42:36.281 --> 42:38.200
Only a crazy person can see herself.

42:39.120 --> 42:41.361
You are just too lonely.

42:41.401 --> 42:44.001
You should let Qingshuang stay with you.

42:44.321 --> 42:45.120
Quiet!

42:45.640 --> 42:46.881
All of you, get to work!

42:47.441 --> 42:48.240
Your Highness,

42:48.401 --> 42:50.321
are you going out without breakfast?

42:50.321 --> 42:51.720
Did you drive her away?

42:51.881 --> 42:53.040
Did she go back to Lishan?

42:53.801 --> 42:55.921
Prince Ding is now
the Pacification Commissioner

42:56.361 --> 42:58.160
and granted a banner of authority.

42:58.401 --> 43:00.481
He shall bring 50 bolts of silk,
100 taels of gold,

43:00.481 --> 43:01.921
and a box of century-old ginseng

43:02.361 --> 43:04.761
(Lishan Academy)
to visit Lishan on behalf of His Majesty

43:05.080 --> 43:06.481
to demonstrate the imperial grace.

43:14.736 --> 43:21.328
ظآزMemories hold you back
from fulfilling your dreamsظآز

43:24.912 --> 43:31.056
ظآزOnly by moving forward
can you find reunionظآز

43:33.264 --> 43:36.496
ظآزEndings only mark new routesظآز

43:36.720 --> 43:42.736
ظآزIt's all part of the sceneryظآز

43:43.056 --> 43:46.480
ظآزTo the horizon's callظآز

43:46.544 --> 43:53.104
ظآزYour journey hasn't startedظآز

43:54.160 --> 43:58.096
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

43:58.096 --> 44:03.792
ظآزBoth joy and grief
make the trip worthwhileظآز

44:04.304 --> 44:12.912
ظآزTrying to catch up
to your own lost shadowظآز

44:13.808 --> 44:19.312
ظآزWithin the wilds, echoes thriveظآز

44:19.312 --> 44:24.816
ظآزClear mind leads to a clear pathظآز

44:24.880 --> 44:28.944
ظآزBe grateful to your lossesظآز

44:29.232 --> 44:34.456
ظآزMake your steps weightlessظآز

44:35.056 --> 44:38.768
ظآزTowards mountains,
chase the stars brightظآز

44:38.800 --> 44:44.464
ظآزLet time embrace you
and wash away the pastظآز

44:45.232 --> 44:53.200
ظآزPut every twist behind you,
drift leisurely through timeظآز

44:54.608 --> 44:59.856
ظآزMake headway against the wind,
let mountains bow to your paceظآز

45:00.112 --> 45:06.016
ظآزRush towards a life without regretظآز

45:06.016 --> 45:10.136
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:10.352 --> 45:15.088
ظآزUnbound by formظآز

45:16.304 --> 45:20.576
ظآزLet your nature burst freeظآز

45:20.816 --> 45:26.256
ظآزUnbound by formظآز
